Simple erlang single-connection TCP client
====

<a name='introduction'>

Introduction
------------

Simple single-connection TCP client for queuing requests towards a single socket
and having automatic reconnection. Also supports failover to multiple configured
endpoints

License is GNUBL.

Copyright can be granted after providing author with beer.

Usage
-----

Include as a rebar dependency and start the gen_server under your apps
supervisor. The API is trivial; see typespecs in the module for the exported
functions.